Hey hey! 

It has been a MINUTE since I have been on the podcast. Tune in to hear:

-Where I've been

-A convo on the New Moon in Leo tonight 7/28/2022 + Fears of Being Seen

- How to work with me (join the waitlist for high level coaching on how to go from single + frustrated---> Attracting the relationship of your desire)

Beatricekamau.com/Womanofdesire

-DM to inquire about 1:1 coaching

Please block and report the IG account @thesSelflovefix with TWO S's

My ONLY instagram account is @theselflovefix I would not DM you to solicit readings or sessions, those are scam accounts. Please block and report anyone who DMs you impersonating me and soliciting readings.
